'''Kris Rinne''' is a technology person and retired Senior VP of network technology at [[AT&T Labs]]. She was an inductee to the 2013 Wireless Hall of Fame<ref>[http://www.fiercewireless.com/story/atts-rinne-retire-keathley-take-over-network-planning/2014-09-02 Fierce Wireless]</ref> and the 2014 [[List of Women in Technology International Hall of Fame inductees|Women in Technology International Hall of Fame]]. She has been described as a key person in wireless technologies for her AT&T work.<ref>[http://www.witi.com/center/witimuseum/halloffame/328137/Kris-Rinne-Senior-Vice-President,-Network-&-Product-Planning-AT&T-Services,-Inc./ WITI Hall of Fame page]</ref>

