The '''''Ministerio de Educación Superior, Ciencia y Tecnología''''' (MESCYT) (Ministry of Higher Education, Science and Technology) is a government institution that regulates [[higher education]] in the [[Dominican Republic]]. It was formerly known as the ''Consejo Nacional de Educación Superior'' (CONES) (National Council of Higher Education). The current minister is [[Alejandrina Germán]], who entered the position in August 2016.<ref>{{cite web |title=Danilo Medina juramenta a nuevo Gabinete: Los designa a través de decreto |url=https://presidencia.gob.do/noticias/danilo-medina-juramenta-nuevo-gabinete-los-designa-traves-de-decreto |website=Presidencia de la República Dominicana |accessdate=6 June 2018 |language=es |date=16 August 2016}}</ref>
