{{Prehistoric Asia}} {{Navbox prehistoric caves}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:Yuchanyan}} [[Category:Neolithic China]] [[Category:History of ceramics]] [[Category:Caves of Hunan]] [[Category:Major National Historical and Cultural Sites in Hunan]] [[Category:Dao County]]
